Class Kvp
'========1=========2=========3=========4=========5=========6=========7=========8=========9=========A=========B=========C
' Code line limit should be 120 characters.
' Comment line limit should be 80 characters
'========1=========2=========3=========4=========5=========6=========7=========8=========9=========A=========B=========C
